               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 3ra-43rb)
 - Bǝsrāta Mātewos “Gospel of
                     Matthew” (fols. 3ra-43rb)
 - Short postscript (fol. 43rb)
 II) Gospel
                     of Mark (fols. 44ra-66vb)
 - Bǝsrāta Mārqos “Gospel of Mark” (fols.
                     44ra-66vb)
 III) Gospel of Luke (fols. 68ra-110rb)
 - Bǝsrāta Luqās
                     “Gospel of Luke” (fols. 68ra-110rb)
 - Postscript (fol. 110rb)
 IV)
                     Gospel of John (fols. 110va-143ra)
 - Biography of John (fol.
                     110va-vb)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of John: 20 titles (fol.
                     110vb)
 - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols. 111ra-142vb)
 -
                     Postscript (fol. 143ra)
 
 Additiones 1-8.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title>The "Golden Gospel" of Dabra salām Qǝddus Mikāʾel Nǝḥbi gädam</title>
